, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1012730, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "Peace be with you O Noble Master. Peace be with you O one whom God honoured with veneration. Peace be with you O grandfather of the best of all mortals. Peace be with you O son of the chosen Prophets. Peace be with you O son of the beloved vicegerents. Peace be with you O Master of the Meccans sanctuary. Peace be with you O heir of the maqam of Ibrahim.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay sayyade sheriff aap par salaam ho. Ay Ibrahim'e Khaleel (a.s) ke shajre (generation) ki phal-daar shaakh aap par salaam ho. Ay duniya mein behtareen aadmi ke jade buzurg-waar aap par salaamo ho. Ay muntakhab ambiya ke farzand aap par salaamo ho. Ay ausiya o auliya ke farzand aap par salaamo ho.", "Urdu": "اے سید شریف آپ پر سلام ہو، اے ابراہیم خلیل کے شجرہ کی پھل دار شاخ آپ پر سلام ہو، اے دنیا میں بہترین آدمی کے جد بزرگوار آپ پر سلام ہو، اے منتخب انبیاء کے فرزند آپ پر سلام ہو، اے اوصیاء الاولیاء کے فرزند آپ پر سلام ہو۔", "RArabic": "ASSALAAMO A’LAIKA AYYO-HAS SAYYE-DUN NABEELO. ASSALAAMO A’LAIKA AYYO-HAL GHUS-NUL MUS-MERO MIN SHAJARA-TE IBRAAHEE-MAL KHALEE-LE. ASSALAAMO A’LAIKA YAA JADDA KHAIY-RIL WA-RAA. ASSALAAMO A’LAIKA YABNAL AMBE-YAAA-IL ASFE-YAAA-E. ASSALAAMO A’LAIKA YABNAL AWSE-YAAA-IL AWLE-YAAA-E.", "ArabicText1": "اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَیْكَ اَیُّہَا السَّیِّدُ النَّبِیْلُ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَیْكَ اَیُّہَا الْغُصْنُ الْمُثْمِرُ مِنْ شَجَرَۃِ اِبْرَاہِیْمَ الْخَلِیْلِ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَیْكَ یَا جَدَّ خَیْرِ الْوَرٰی۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَیْكَ یَابْنَ الْاَنْبِیَآئِ الْاَصْفِیَآئِ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَیْكَ یَابْنَ الْاَوْصِیَآئِ الْاَوْلِیَآئِ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1012731, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "Peace be with you O (the one) entrusted with the might house of God. Peace be with you O splendid one of the highborn. O one who is high through the perfection of qualities. Peace be with you O Master of the Quraish known as Abd Manaf. Peace be with you and your preceding forefathers who were representatives of God in the worlds, and His mercy and His blessings.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay haram'e Ilaahi ke sardaar aap par salaamo ho. Ay maqaam'e Ibrahim (a.s) ke waaris aap par salaamo ho. Ay Khudaaye azeem ke ghar ke muhaafiz aur mutawalli aap par salaamo ho aura ap kea aba o ajdaad par aur aap ke paak o paakeeza farzand par salaam ho aur Khuda ki rehmat aur Uski barkate’n ho.", "Urdu": "اے حرم الہٰی کے سردار آپ پر سلام ہو، اے مقام ابراہیم کے وارث آپ پر سلام ہو۔ اے خدائے عظیم کے گھر کے محافظ اور متولی آپ پر سلام ہو، اور آپ کے آبا و اجداد پر اور آپ کے پاک و پاکیزہ فرزندوں پر سلام ہو اور خدا کی رحمت اور اس کی برکتیں ہوں۔", "RArabic": "ASSALAAMO A’LAIKA YAA SAYYE-DAL HARA-ME. ASSALAAMO A’LAIKA YAA WAARESA MAQAA-ME IBRAAHEEMA. ASSALAAMO A’LAIKA YAA SAAHEBA BAIYTIL LAA-HIL A’ZEE-ME. ASSALAAMO A’LAIKA WA A’LAA AAA-BAA'e KA WA ABNAAA'e KAT TAAHE-REENA WA RAH-MATUL LAAHE WA BARA-KAATO-HU.", "ArabicText1": "اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَیْكَ یَا سَیِّدَ الْحَرَمِ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَیْكَ یَا وَارِثَ مَقَامِ اِبْرَاہِیْمَ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَیْكَ یَا صَاحِبَ بَیْتِ اللهِ الْعَظِیْمِ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَیْكَ وَعَلٰی آبَائِكَ وَاَبْنَآئِكَ الطَّاہِرِیْنَ وَرَحْمَۃُ اللهِ وَبَرَكَاتُہٗ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "Arab